<h2>Creating The Meta Box</h2>
<p>To create the meta box, we'll take advantage of <a>the <code>add_meta_box</code> function</a> as documented in the WordPress Codex.&nbsp;To do this, we're going to be introducing a new class, updating the plugin's bootstrap file, and introducing some views that will be used to render markup in the browser.</p>
